<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title> <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="page-content">
        <h1>환영합니다! 쥬얼리 쇼핑몰 메인 페이지입니다.</h1>
        <p>오늘의 추천 상품을 확인해보세요.</p>
        
        <section class="product-list">
            <% if (products && products.length > 0) { %>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px;">
                    <% products.forEach(product => { %>
                        <div class="product-item" style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;">
                            <h3><%= product.name %></h3>
                            <p>가격: <%= product.price %>원</p>
                            <a href="/products/<%= product.id %>">상세보기</a>
                        </div>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <p>등록된 상품이 없습니다.</p>
            <% } %>
        </section>

        <% if (locals.dbTime) { %>
            <p>DB Status: <%= dbTime %></p>
        <% } %>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>